NAME
       __gnu_parallel::parallel_tag - Recommends parallel execution at compile time, optionally using a user-specified number of threads.

SYNOPSIS
       #include <tags.h>

       Inherited by __gnu_parallel::balanced_quicksort_tag, __gnu_parallel::balanced_tag, __gnu_parallel::default_parallel_tag, __gnu_parallel::exact_tag, __gnu_parallel::multiway_mergesort_exact_tag,
